SUMMARY:Best Of
DESCRIPTION:TechTO\n\\*\\*This is a paid event\, please register via our Luma Page. You need to have a ticket in order to attend this event: https://luma.com/bestof-apr-13-2026\n\n**Best Of TechTO is our annual night to celebrate what Toronto’s tech community is building - and to meet the people behind it.**\n\nSince day one\, 700+ founders have taken the TechTO stage and 60\,000+ community members have shown up with the same goal: learn something new\, meet someone new.\n\nThis year we’re bringing Best Of to **Toronto City Hall** for an evening of founder stories\, live demos\, standout showcases\, and the kind of conversations that don’t happen on Slack. Great food + drinks included - all under those iconic arches.
